      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON JOY (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.95) at The Gardens behind Gretzky in a Grade 5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Leading chance again. NOVA LASS (2) finished second (22.40) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th there. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Worth following up. MY HARLEY (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Barbie Zeal (22.46) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Winning chance. RUBY JUAN (4) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
